spec_data.Name: php-zendframework-zend-servicemanager
spec_data.Description:
The Service Locator design pattern is implemented by the Zend\ServiceManager
component. The Service Locator is a service/object locator, tasked with
retrieving other objects.

Documentation: https://zendframework.github.io/zend-servicemanager/
